msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/simd-for-faster-computing.md:106
msgid ""
"Beyond that, you may never write any of this yourself, but as always, the "
"libraries you depend on may. For example, the regex crate contains these "
"SIMD speedups without you needing to do anything at all!"
msgstr ""
